<p>Reports invalid prefixes defined in the <code>@ConfigurationProperties</code> annotations:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Missing prefix</li>
  <li>Empty prefix</li>
  <li>Duplicate prefix</li>
  <li>Prefix in notation other than kebab-case</li>
</ul>
<p>
  The inspection triggers in classes that are annotated with <code>@ConfigurationProperties</code> and not registered via <code>@EnableConfigurationProperties</code>,
  marked as Spring component, or scanned via <code>@ConfigurationPropertiesScan</code>.</p>
<!-- tooltip end -->
<p>
  This inspection only triggers in classes annotated with <code>@ConfigurationProperties</code> that are not scanned via <code>@ConfigurationPropertiesScan</code>
  when the Spring Boot version for the project or module is set to 2.2.0 or later.
</p>
<p><small>New in 2018.3</small></p>
